articles.title: Rare hybrid solar eclipse stuns Australia, Indonesia skywatchers - Fox News
articles.description: Eclipse watchers gathered in Australia, Indonesia and East Timor to catch a glimpse of a rare hybrid solar eclipse that sent temperatures falling and plunged areas into darkness.
